Fatal error: Class dog may not inherit from final class (animal) in
```

```
<?php 
class animal{
	public $name='动物';
	final public function jiao(){
		echo $this->name."会叫<br>";
	}
}

class dog extends animal{
	public $name='狗';
	public function jiao(){
		echo $this->name."会叫<br>";
	}
